data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN @ 3.5% for Veterans Only!  Desirable corner lot on cul-de-sac that backs up to greenbelt, PebbleTec play pool with rock waterfall and new pool deck resurface (2023). New vinyl wood plank flooring/baseboard (2021), new roof (2022), addition of patio cover (2022), new paver patio extension and walkways includes string lights and fans (2023), installed can lights in the kitchen, Solar added 2022. Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and new ceiling fans. The sellers mentioned they will certainly miss their Arizona home especially relaxing in the quiet backyard, enjoying the refreshing pool and the mountain views across the green space behind the home. You will love this well maintained home!
